com.kuka.geometry.listeners

Interface IRedundancyInformationListener


  • public interface IRedundancyInformationListener
    Interface for a listener that is notified when redundancy information of an ObjectFrame changes.

    This listener is notified each time redundancy information was added or removed or if a redundancy information value was changed. It is also notified when these changes occur on a descendant of the object the listener is registered at.

    • Method Summary
